Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:00:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才提到说要初吻而已 结果她就跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还提初吻 你也太厚脸皮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得如果说自己是第一次\N那样的话印象不是会比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种谎话 人家光靠直觉就能看穿的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而会是那种更让人不敢信任的典型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定，那时候的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第30话 “裸足的少女”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能够烤成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生真是什么都会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃过再夸奖不是比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会烤蛋糕的男人很少见嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好，我是筱原若叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会挑时间的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个蛋糕是晓生先生做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用，不过味道不保证就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生真是什么都会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句话我刚才已经说过了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是请先吃吃看再夸奖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会烤蛋糕的男人很少见嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句刚才我也说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么觉得你是故意漏我气的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你说过\N晓生先生已经有未婚妻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，喜欢的心情和那没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔？是喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在谈什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 没有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那会是少女们的坏心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果一直这么死脑筋的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会连恋爱都谈不成的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是像个女孩子一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么说是为了你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这什么男生制服 可是一点都不好看的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，大家都说这样挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家说又怎样！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的关键是我这生活指导老师所决定的品味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算老师这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请教务主任也严正的说说她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不遵守校规的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子还是该穿着轻盈飘逸的裙子才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁决定的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这、这不是理事长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓、晓生先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！不，我是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教务主任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的国中部恳亲会让我也参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老早就想和理事长一起促膝长谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有，理事长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次提到有关…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去阿姆斯特丹姊妹校的视察团成员人选…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，也许最近遴选委员会就会发出正式的通知了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦请您让我的名字也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会记在心上的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外，我有点事想找她谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把学生借给我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了…理事长…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是他的容姿… 还是穿着打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，还有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太常以校规为理由去拘束学生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论如何…都请以尊重学生自主性的方式进行辅导
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我谈的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小傻瓜，没有什么事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也是你那身威风凛凛装扮的迷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再者，你面对那些啰唆的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然不改变自己信念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我感到有某种坚强与崇高…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长可以说那种话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我妹妹…不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…这样的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，我在想什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家晓生先生已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉最近好像常看到这部车耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是今年的热门车款嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧－蒂－娜－
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，筱原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话请不要叫我筱原 叫我若叶就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人居然偷偷的一起出场 这可不太寻常喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成等下要约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然碰在一起罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，晓生先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起去兜风呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像今天这样在这碰到 一定也是某种缘份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明最近每天都跑来玩还敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一辈子当作回忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就两个小时也可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会强迫人的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准！不准！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜不用跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为约会是指单独两个人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对，晓生先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔，请慢走…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好美的回忆喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海好漂亮… 风的感觉也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是最棒的约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想你应该也知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有未婚妻了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 难得人家正在陶醉的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是兜兜风而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是在吃醋吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这、这才不可能呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早啊，姬宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安，欧蒂娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的明明是王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明只喜欢送我这枚戒指的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我会如此地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里会是这么的小鹿乱撞呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，你是怎么啦？ 居然会犯那种错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确…我到底是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗？欧蒂娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…抱歉，还让你照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是赶快去保健室冰敷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说姬宫啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，欧蒂娜大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:12:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，上车吧 去医院好好检查一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他事就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让姬宫也一起搭又有什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会是只能单独两个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你朋友告诉我的，不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先走了，安希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…晓生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让你陪我一起去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不都已经和家人一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼…是在明年春天对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是很好的人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香苗小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是医生说今天还是不要走路比较好的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦！我还能走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要勉强的好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我背你吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生是花花公子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你很会讨女孩子欢心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…该说是… 不像理事长的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让人觉得是有点危险的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是不喜欢听从命令而穿着男生制服吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可能是同类吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的情形… 是因为王子的关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了想和从前就喜欢上的王子重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其背着走，还是用抱的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋鞋鞋鞋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快扔了那双鞋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要我把重要的红鞋给…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是穿上的话 你会非跳舞跳到死不可的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道这样不行 却一样会去做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来，你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上也不拿着和我一样的红鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这，这个… 我只是拿着而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会穿上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不穿还拿在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了！真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都拿着还不穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费的是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您肚子会饿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么问？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看您今天的晚餐 好像几乎都没吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有点没食欲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若叶那个家伙她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前若叶那个家伙说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说没有不能谈的恋爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢人的心情是无法自拔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是有不可以喜欢上的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我并不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也像若叶所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于喜欢的这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样有着连我自己都不知如何是好的部份在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样子的吗？果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你也有喜欢的人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有我的王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧你是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天上欧蒂娜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玻璃鞋的主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一提…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也为她着迷是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决斗被打败时，我还大受打击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是因为被打败的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说居然有个少女动摇了我的信念…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子里还让我因此而思考着今后的生存方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有眼光…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会成为好女人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是啊…理事长…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天好像没吃什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是身体不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我怎么了 这我该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香苗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难得，在这一大早…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这么早怎么逮的到你？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近比较忙的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙着看星星吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安，香苗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊，安希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道何时你才肯改口叫我嫂嫂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？你是…那个… 欧蒂娜同学对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃早餐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 倒是说…我母亲来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岳母大人来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了，晓生先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岳母大人…真是难得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点话…想和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是什么事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作应该都很顺利的在进行的才是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是电话里头不方便谈的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生…\N最近你是不是在躲我的女儿 躲着香苗是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能接手这个学园
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是和我女儿结婚后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别忘了婚约这种事 是随时都可以取消的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对香苗小姐一直都很体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至到若是发现彗星的话\N还想用她的名字命名的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闻，这是香苗喜欢的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都擦着她要我擦的香水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在只有两人的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长还康健吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种男人怎么样都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才是喔… 是我的王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说！听我说！欧蒂娜 我终于见到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生的未婚妻凤香苗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是个漂亮的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人长得美，头脑看起来也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上她还是个大小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这种人，的确会有小小的赢不了她的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的…可是王子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫我记得你是AB型的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于让人摸不清楚\N又不大会吐露心事的类型是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 欧蒂娜大人是B型对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B型是…以自我为中心又非常爱钻牛角尖…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，真是不好意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来七实为什么会寄住到我们的房间来？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.13,0:23:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为七实也是B型的关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.07,0:23:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看来的确是非常爱钻牛角尖没错啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回　少女革命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“她的悲剧”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对命运默示录
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

